The sdoc scripts in this directory generate XML DTD documentation of selected DTDs.

Before you can use the sdoc scripts in this directory, make sure that
the DTDs are parsed.

Some selected DTDs are found in  tools/dtd-parser/dtds  in your laml dir.
Activate the appropriate parsing scripts, such as svg11-parser.laml, before you attempt
to generate documentation.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SVG manual:
Make it by the local LAML script 

   svg11-mirror.sdoc

XHTML1.1 manual
   xhtml11-mirror.sdoc

XHTML 1.0 manuals (strict, frameset, transitional):
   xhtml10-strict-mirror.sdoc
   xhtml10-transitional-mirror.sdoc
   xhtml10-frameset-mirror.sdoc


